{"thig15.1:0.1":"Therigatha 15.1 ","thig15.1:0.2":"Cattalisanipata ","thig15.1:0.3":"Isidasitherigatha ","thig15.1:1.1":"Nagaramhi kusumaname, ","thig15.1:1.2":"Pataliputtamhi pathaviya mande; ","thig15.1:1.3":"Sakyakulakulinayo, ","thig15.1:1.4":"Dve bhikkhuniyo hi gunavatiyo. ","thig15.1:2.1":"Isidasi tattha eka, ","thig15.1:2.2":"Dutiya bodhiti silasampanna ca; ","thig15.1:2.3":"Jhanajjhayanaratayo, ","thig15.1:2.4":"Bahussutayo dhutakilesayo. ","thig15.1:3.1":"Ta pindaya caritva, ","thig15.1:3.2":"Bhattattham kariya dhotapattayo; ","thig15.1:3.3":"Rahitamhi sukhanisinna, ","thig15.1:3.4":"Ima gira abbhudiresum. ","thig15.1:4.1":"“Pasadikasi ayye, ","thig15.1:4.2":"Isidasi vayopi te aparihino; ","thig15.1:4.3":"Kim disvana byalikam, ","thig15.1:4.4":"Athasi nekkhammamanuyutta”. ","thig15.1:5.1":"Evamanuyunjiyamana sa, ","thig15.1:5.2":"Rahite dhammadesanakusala; ","thig15.1:5.3":"Isidasi vacanamabravi, ","thig15.1:5.4":"“Suna bodhi yathamhi pabbajita”. ","thig15.1:6.1":"“Ujjeniya puravare, ","thig15.1:6.2":"Mayham pita silasamvuto setthi; ","thig15.1:6.3":"Tassamhi ekadhita, ","thig15.1:6.4":"Piya manapa ca dayita ca. ","thig15.1:7.1":"Atha me saketato varaka, ","thig15.1:7.2":"Agacchumuttamakulina; ","thig15.1:7.3":"Setthi pahutaratano, ","thig15.1:7.4":"Tassa mamam sunhamadasi tato. ","thig15.1:8.1":"Sassuya sasurassa ca, ","thig15.1:8.2":"Sayam patam panamamupagamma; ","thig15.1:8.3":"Sirasa karomi pade, ","thig15.1:8.4":"Vandami yathamhi anusittha. ","thig15.1:9.1":"Ya mayham samikassa, ","thig15.1:9.2":"Bhaginiyo bhatuno parijano va; ","thig15.1:9.3":"Tamekavarakampi disva, ","thig15.1:9.4":"Ubbigga asanam demi. ","thig15.1:10.1":"Annena ca panena ca, ","thig15.1:10.2":"Khajjena ca yanca tattha sannihitam; ","thig15.1:10.3":"Chademi upanayami ca, ","thig15.1:10.4":"Demi ca yam yassa patirupam. ","thig15.1:11.1":"Kalena upatthahitva, ","thig15.1:11.2":"Gharam samupagamami ummare; ","thig15.1:11.3":"Dhovanti hatthapade, ","thig15.1:11.4":"Panjalika samikamupemi. ","thig15.1:12.1":"Koccham pasadam anjaninca, ","thig15.1:12.2":"Adasakanca ganhitva; ","thig15.1:12.3":"Parikammakarika viya, ","thig15.1:12.4":"Sayameva patim vibhusemi. ","thig15.1:13.1":"Sayameva odanam sadhayami, ","thig15.1:13.2":"Sayameva bhajanam dhovanti; ","thig15.1:13.3":"Matava ekaputtakam, ","thig15.1:13.4":"Tatha bhattaram paricarami. ","thig15.1:14.1":"Evam mam bhattikatam, ","thig15.1:14.2":"Anurattam karikam nihatamanam; ","thig15.1:14.3":"Utthayikam analasam, ","thig15.1:14.4":"Silavatim dussate bhatta. ","thig15.1:15.1":"So mataranca pitaranca, ","thig15.1:15.2":"Bhanati ‘apucchaham gamissami; ","thig15.1:15.3":"Isidasiya na saha vaccham, ","thig15.1:15.4":"Ekagareham saha vatthum’. ","thig15.1:16.1":"‘Ma evam putta avaca, ","thig15.1:16.2":"Isidasi pandita paribyatta; ","thig15.1:16.3":"Utthayika analasa, ","thig15.1:16.4":"Kim tuyham na rocate putta’. ","thig15.1:17.1":"‘Na ca me himsati kinci, ","thig15.1:17.2":"Na caham isidasiya saha vaccham; ","thig15.1:17.3":"Dessava me alam me, ","thig15.1:17.4":"Apucchaham gamissami’. ","thig15.1:18.1":"Tassa vacanam sunitva, ","thig15.1:18.2":"Sassu sasuro ca mam apucchimsu; ","thig15.1:18.3":"‘Kissa taya aparaddham, ","thig15.1:18.4":"Bhana vissattha yathabhutam’. ","thig15.1:19.1":"‘Napiham aparajjham kinci, ","thig15.1:19.2":"Napi himsemi na bhanami dubbacanam; ","thig15.1:19.3":"Kim sakka katuyye, ","thig15.1:19.4":"Yam mam viddessate bhatta’. ","thig15.1:20.1":"Te mam pitugharam patinayimsu, ","thig15.1:20.2":"Vimana dukhena adhibhuta; ","thig15.1:20.3":"Puttamanurakkhamana, ","thig15.1:20.4":"‘Jitamhase rupinim lakkhim’. ","thig15.1:21.1":"Atha mam adasi tato, ","thig15.1:21.2":"Addhassa gharamhi dutiyakulikassa; ","thig15.1:21.3":"Tato upaddhasunkena, ","thig15.1:21.4":"Yena mam vindatha setthi. ","thig15.1:22.1":"Tassapi gharamhi masam, ","thig15.1:22.2":"Avasim atha sopi mam paticcharayi; ","thig15.1:22.3":"Dasiva upatthahantim, ","thig15.1:22.4":"Adusikam silasampannam. ","thig15.1:23.1":"Bhikkhaya ca vicarantam, ","thig15.1:23.2":"Damakam dantam me pita bhanati; ","thig15.1:23.3":"‘Hohisi me jamata, ","thig15.1:23.4":"Nikkhipa potthinca ghatikanca’. ","thig15.1:24.1":"Sopi vasitva pakkham, ","thig15.1:24.2":"Atha tatam bhanati ‘dehi me potthim; ","thig15.1:24.3":"Ghatikanca mallakanca, ","thig15.1:24.4":"Punapi bhikkham carissami’. ","thig15.1:25.1":"Atha nam bhanati tato, ","thig15.1:25.2":"Amma sabbo ca me natiganavaggo; ","thig15.1:25.3":"‘Kim te na kirati idha, ","thig15.1:25.4":"Bhana khippam tam te karihi’ti. ","thig15.1:26.1":"Evam bhanito bhanati, ","thig15.1:26.2":"‘Yadi me atta sakkoti alam mayham; ","thig15.1:26.3":"Isidasiya na saha vaccham, ","thig15.1:26.4":"Ekaghareham saha vatthum’. ","thig15.1:27.1":"Vissajjito gato so, ","thig15.1:27.2":"Ahampi ekakini vicintemi; ","thig15.1:27.3":"‘Apucchituna gaccham, ","thig15.1:27.4":"Marituye va pabbajissam va’. ","thig15.1:28.1":"Atha ayya jinadatta, ","thig15.1:28.2":"Agacchi gocaraya caramana; ","thig15.1:28.3":"Tatakulam vinayadhari, ","thig15.1:28.4":"Bahussuta silasampanna. ","thig15.1:29.1":"Tam disvana amhakam, ","thig15.1:29.2":"Utthayasanam tassa pannapayim; ","thig15.1:29.3":"Nisinnaya ca pade, ","thig15.1:29.4":"Vanditva bhojanamadasim. ","thig15.1:30.1":"Annena ca panena ca, ","thig15.1:30.2":"Khajjena ca yanca tattha sannihitam; ","thig15.1:30.3":"Santappayitva avacam, ","thig15.1:30.4":"‘Ayye icchami pabbajitum’. ","thig15.1:31.1":"Atha mam bhanati tato, ","thig15.1:31.2":"‘Idheva puttaka carahi tvam dhammam; ","thig15.1:31.3":"Annena ca panena ca, ","thig15.1:31.4":"Tappaya samane dvijati ca’. ","thig15.1:32.1":"Athaham bhanami tatam, ","thig15.1:32.2":"Rodanti anjalim panametva; ","thig15.1:32.3":"‘Papanhi maya pakatam, ","thig15.1:32.4":"Kammam tam nijjaressami’. ","thig15.1:33.1":"Atha mam bhanati tato, ","thig15.1:33.2":"‘Papuna bodhinca aggadhammanca; ","thig15.1:33.3":"Nibbananca labhassu, ","thig15.1:33.4":"Yam sacchikari dvipadasettho’. ","thig15.1:34.1":"Matapitu abhivadayitva, ","thig15.1:34.2":"Sabbanca natiganavaggam; ","thig15.1:34.3":"Sattaham pabbajita, ","thig15.1:34.4":"Tisso vijja aphassayim. ","thig15.1:35.1":"Janami attano satta, ","thig15.1:35.2":"Jatiyo yassayam phalavipako; ","thig15.1:35.3":"Tam tava acikkhissam, ","thig15.1:35.4":"Tam ekamana nisamehi. ","thig15.1:36.1":"Nagaramhi erakacche, ","thig15.1:36.2":"Suvannakaro aham pahutadhano; ","thig15.1:36.3":"Yobbanamadena matto, ","thig15.1:36.4":"So paradaram aseviham. ","thig15.1:37.1":"Soham tato cavitva, ","thig15.1:37.2":"Nirayamhi apaccisam ciram; ","thig15.1:37.3":"Pakko tato ca utthahitva, ","thig15.1:37.4":"Makkatiya kucchimokkamim. ","thig15.1:38.1":"Sattahajatakam mam, ","thig15.1:38.2":"Mahakapi yuthapo nillacchesi; ","thig15.1:38.3":"Tassetam kammaphalam, ","thig15.1:38.4":"Yathapi gantvana paradaram. ","thig15.1:39.1":"Soham tato cavitva, ","thig15.1:39.2":"Kalam karitva sindhavaranne; ","thig15.1:39.3":"Kanaya ca khanjaya ca, ","thig15.1:39.4":"Elakiya kucchimokkamim. ","thig15.1:40.1":"Dvadasa vassani aham, ","thig15.1:40.2":"Nillacchito darake parivahitva; ","thig15.1:40.3":"Kiminavatto akallo, ","thig15.1:40.4":"Yathapi gantvana paradaram. ","thig15.1:41.1":"Soham tato cavitva, ","thig15.1:41.2":"Govanijakassa gaviya jato; ","thig15.1:41.3":"Vaccho lakhatambo, ","thig15.1:41.4":"Nillacchito dvadase mase. ","thig15.1:42.1":"Vodhuna nangalamaham, ","thig15.1:42.2":"Sakatanca dharayami; ","thig15.1:42.3":"Andhovatto akallo, ","thig15.1:42.4":"Yathapi gantvana paradaram. ","thig15.1:43.1":"Soham tato cavitva, ","thig15.1:43.2":"Vithiya dasiya ghare jato; ","thig15.1:43.3":"Neva mahila na puriso, ","thig15.1:43.4":"Yathapi gantvana paradaram. ","thig15.1:44.1":"Timsativassamhi mato, ","thig15.1:44.2":"Sakatikakulamhi darika jata; ","thig15.1:44.3":"Kapanamhi appabhoge, ","thig15.1:44.4":"Dhanika purisapatabahulamhi. ","thig15.1:45.1":"Tam mam tato satthavaho, ","thig15.1:45.2":"Ussannaya vipulaya vaddhiya; ","thig15.1:45.3":"Okaddhati vilapantim, ","thig15.1:45.4":"Acchinditva kulagharasma. ","thig15.1:46.1":"Atha solasame vasse, ","thig15.1:46.2":"Disva mam pattayobbanam kannam; ","thig15.1:46.3":"Orundhatassa putto, ","thig15.1:46.4":"Giridaso nama namena. ","thig15.1:47.1":"Tassapi anna bhariya, ","thig15.1:47.2":"Silavati gunavati yasavati ca; ","thig15.1:47.3":"Anuratta bhattaram, ","thig15.1:47.4":"Tassaham viddesanamakasim. ","thig15.1:48.1":"Tassetam kammaphalam, ","thig15.1:48.2":"Yam mam apakirituna gacchanti; ","thig15.1:48.3":"Dasiva upatthahantim, ","thig15.1:48.4":"Tassapi anto kato maya”ti. ","thig15.1:49.1":"… Isidasi theri …. ","thig15.1:50.1":"Cattalisanipato nitthito. "}